From:
--Original Message---
Sent:
Monday, October 08, 2001 2:09 PM
Moore, Tamara
To:
Chaikin, Karen
Subject: Don Jose ad backgrounder
Importance:
High
Karen:
We are in the process of creating materials about the corporate advertising efforts to post to the web site (the
press room). Specifically, we are posting images from the TV and print ads, as well as the scripts for the radio
spots. We will also post the backgrounders with the TV ads. We have crafted and had approved the
backgrounders for Sam and Martin's Newsstand, but had not drafted one for the Hispanic TV We Card spot, "Don
Jose." I have drafted one now based on your feedback on the other 2 ad backgrounders, and am sending it to you
for approval. Pis. take a look at it and let me know if you have edits. I've also attached Sam and Martin's
Newsstand for reference. Thanks, Karen.
